1️⃣ VTT/SRT File Upload Module

Implement the UI to upload VTT and SRT files with proper validation, status indication, and integration with the backend processing flow.

2️⃣ AI Result Generation Integration

Integrate frontend workflow to trigger and display generated results (Summary, Keywords, and Assessment Questions) for the selected file.

3️⃣ File Management Dashboard

Develop a file management interface with listing, filtering, and delete functionality for uploaded files.

4️⃣ Workspace Result Viewing Interface

Design and implement a structured workspace to display:

Summary

Keywords

Assessment Questions
with organized layout and expandable viewing options.

5️⃣ Result Interaction & Export Features

Enable interactive capabilities including:

Expand mode view

Edit functionality (Summary & Keywords)

Copy to clipboard

Download generated content
